			<div class="smallfont">TIE Fighter Pilot</div>
			
		
			
				<div class="smallfont">
					&nbsp;<br /><a href="member.php?s=9ba3a04946ea35d5e8e50219fa203069&amp;u=33470"><img src="image.php?s=9ba3a04946ea35d5e8e50219fa203069&amp;u=33470&amp;dateline=1108442465" alt="Global Nexus's Avatar" border="0" /></a>
